name: Hamilton Utilities YIELD MAXIMIZER TM ETF
longDescription: UMAX is designed for attractive monthly income, while providing exposure to a portfolio of utility services equity securities, primarily domiciled/ listed in Canada and the U.S. To reduce volatility and augment dividend income, UMAX will employ an active covered call strategy. The investment objective of UMAX is to deliver attractive monthly income.
